Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The northern lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:58.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In the peace of that shrine....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...lies a legendary Holy Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wandering through eternity, that Holy Blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...lies there sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:15.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Along History the one who pulls out the Holy Blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be known as a hero and will be given everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:27.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,One strike from it will bring silence to all on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:31.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And a swing of that sword will split the Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow of a figure, soaring with golden wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Truly the shape of a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:43.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What must not be forgotten are all the\N techniques of the Holy Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall forever speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the Holy Blade's dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally speak and pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass on the name of the Holy Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...Excalibur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the present...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:10.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another man stands, challenging to create History.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,His name being...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ox Ford!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:29.15,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(650,180)}The Legend of the\N Holy Sword 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:29.15,Copy of Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(640,676)}~Drunk, Defeated, Bought, A Virtue?~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legend of the Holy Sword 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunk, Defeated, Bought, A Virtue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Holy Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:04.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:06.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,By what name do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ox...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:11.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my looks, I'm one of the top nerds in Shibusen{\fscx280}-{\fscx146.666667}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm not a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My legend started in the 12th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:27.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My legend started in the 12th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to hear my heroic tales?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I came for that purpose and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.65,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:36.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be with me, there are one thousand tasks you must complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to understand them completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but where am I being a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:46.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Again with the "fool?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:54.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My morning starts with a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Heed my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My morning starts with a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as I thought, there can be no morning without roasted green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My morning starts with a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't drinking coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the thousand tasks you must abide to is:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My morning starts with a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm saying that wasn't coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This lady next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, without any doubt, my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}was{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:00.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I was still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The city was quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The people had lost their hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just living with no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:46.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll save up money and leave this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to watch the seven o' clock news everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... In other words, that beautiful girl was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:07:59.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you can't seem to get it do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Item 58 from the thousand tasks you're to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not to speak while I am humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very important task.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:20.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't believe your demands and flashbacks relate to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:20.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:25.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an intimate relationship between the humming and the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your memories of delinquency...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:32.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what's called a fragile ensemble that cannot be comprehended through logic and statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly worthy of being called "destiny."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:34.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was the result of fate that was polished,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...matured, and perfected through complicated chemical reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was to dance in a packed opera house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:48.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...shouldering the burden for the fate of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:49.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nice to do these kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:36.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing nothing in particular, just hanging around with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels very peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's always peaceful, I don't stand out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm to stand out, I definitely must...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:50.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already written the report we were assigned last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't finished it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the report due tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of report...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That report?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but could you give us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to reflect is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:39.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To do anything out of the blue is sheer stupidity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,During that incident, {\alpha&HFF&}my sharp, high intellect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,During that incident, my sharp, high intellect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...needed time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:53.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That happened when I was still living on Baker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, have you figured anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary, my dear Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:05.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we had overlooked a very elementary trick thanks to the culprit's wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But this place was inaccessible from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:09.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, Excalibur-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, that line is the most adequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:18.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us hear it Excalibur-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your deduction to solve the trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and figure out the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:29.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say this was a very simple and a very easy trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:33.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, for a normal person it might not be simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps some may believe it is a complicated, and thus a difficult problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:42.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact of the matter is that it only looks complicated and is actually very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, perhaps some may not see it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:50.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, stating what's difficult and what is not is an extremely delicate problem and{\fscx280}-{\fscx146.666667}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:54.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Excalibur we understand, so what about the trick and the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I am well aware of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we get it so reveal us the trick, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is too elementary, there's no need to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:11.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...I safely solved the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:26.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Watson really the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:31.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with that fact in your mind, let's get to item 278 of the thousand tasks you're to abide to:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:35.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My meals must never contain any carrots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I too don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:37.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:42.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This item 349 of the thousand tasks you're to abide to:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:45.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A Technician must not be picky with his or her food and eat everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:48.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take such self-indulgence a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what about{\fscx280}-{\fscx146.666667}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:54.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what sort of tragedy will befall on you with that kind of attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:58.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely understand if you watch this episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:01.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just when my legend had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My Technician, King Arthur and I were on a journey together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:12.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing this many enemies will be tough even for us, don't you think so, Excalibur?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Arthur, that's not like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That cowardly feeling will lead us to our downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Knights of the Round Table, never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We swore upon that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten that I have comrades of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:33.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of those comrades too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my friend Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Arthur's journey continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You acted differently...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is item 679 of the thousand that you're to abide to:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:08.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You must always have a dehumidifier in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:11.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, by the way, when did you develop that personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on what I've shown you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...you should already know by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...that "hard-boiled" describes me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:23.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone,{\alpha&HFF&} today it's all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, today it's all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Excalibur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an amazing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was feeling dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:53.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...frustration toward being reclusive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and irreplaceable awkwardness spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The emptiness that invaded my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...felt bigger every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that day came....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur, I'm truly happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur, hurry up, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:50.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wish this day would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:08.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:19.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That kindness of yours will one day, surely become a burden to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Cassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur, at the very least remember this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:30.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:38.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}those days of happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,However, those days of happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:44.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...as she said, didn't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:46.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It ends like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The dispute among the two gangs was put on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:58.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words this is deeply related to item 778,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...do not ever send express deliveries via a cash on delivery service,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the thousand tasks you're to abide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened next...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngster...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:12.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm curious about the rest of the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall show respect to your words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sing you a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have to be a song...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:23.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who don't even know how important songs were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the History of cultural history of human beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't have any right to deny a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the fact that you don't have any right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:38.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the aspect of denying me to sing is a very important factor not to be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:42.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:52.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,From the United Kingdom I'm looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to California...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:19:00.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this going to last...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:52.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:56.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I've mostly finished talking to you about the thousand tasks you're to abide to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's of the utmost goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the most important task, number 452.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're to attend to my five hour reading meetings punctually!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:06.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You now have in your grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory and glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory and glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the world in your hands, {\alpha&HFF&}you shall rise and reign as a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the world in your hands, you shall rise and reign as a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let us go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory and glory to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngster, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:45.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a partner and I'll be on my way home now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:47.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:52.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, I tried to write a report on you for homework, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying so I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't finish the report on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star, did you do it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's done alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? That's barely any.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. All you need...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...is one word to describe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:25.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you exactly write?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:28.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:04.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Good news to everyone in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:06.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Technician who wants to be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:09.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like to use me as you wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:12.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's currently limited to just one person to be allowed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:13.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, {\alpha&HFF&}this beautiful form!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, this beautiful form!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:17.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The unimaginable sharpness of the blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:21.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The five hour reading meetings are now only four hours for you to try out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:23.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss out on this big chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:24.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon a fair raffle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:28.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will hang out with just one Technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:30.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact here:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:32.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory and glory to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:34.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:40.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary musicians who've been leading the glam rock world of the UK...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:42.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...are coming to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:50.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhythmical and yet a deep and beautiful melody line fascinates all who turn their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And the title of the song is:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur Goes To California!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:00.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In stores now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:03.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us all your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:03.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:07.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for the preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:09.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Excalibur commotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:12.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...we go back to a serious Soul Eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:16.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Shibusen will be having a foundation anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:18.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll throw a fancy and rich party,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:21.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they're even going to have a blood-stained love-hate play.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:23.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's exactly going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:24.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:26.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Soul Eater episode 18:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:28.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nightmare Before The Festival. And So The Curtain Rises?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.43,0:24:27.43,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,200)\fs79}The Nightmare Before\N The Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.43,0:24:27.43,Copy of Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,666)}~And So, The Curtain Rises?~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:29.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it!
